    public class SimpMessageMappingInfo
extends java.lang.Object
implements MessageCondition<SimpMessageMappingInfo>
    MessageCondition for SImple Messaging Protocols. Encapsulates the following request mapping conditions:
    1. SimpMessageTypeMessageCondition
    2. DestinationPatternsMessageCondition
    从以下版本开始:
    4.0
    作者:
    Rossen Stoyanchev

      • getMatchingCondition

        @Nullable
public SimpMessageMappingInfo getMatchingCondition(Message<?> message)
        从接口复制的说明: MessageCondition
        Check if this condition matches the given Message and returns a potentially new condition with content tailored to the current message. For example a condition with destination patterns might return a new condition with sorted, matching patterns only.
        指定者:
        getMatchingCondition 在接口中 MessageCondition<SimpMessageMappingInfo>
        返回:
